    tmp = (0.15 / wp.cos((v1 + 0.10 - v1 + 0.08)))
    tmp = 0.15
    v1 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.80 + v0 + 0.21)) + v0)
    v2 = wp.cos((0.07 + 0.08))
    v0 = v1
    v2 = v2
    tmp = v0
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.93 - v1 + 0.87)) / wp.exp((v2 + 0.90 + v1 + 0.04)))
